piece of the Celica is undoubtedly the 400hp Ferrari V8, an engine far removed from its original design intentions. The 3.6L motor and its corresponding manual gearbox – still operated by the original Ferrari gated shifter – are suspended in the tube chassis with custom-made mounts and brackets. Streamlining the installation, the water pump and power steering were converted to electric, and an aluminium fuel tank was strategically placed behind the front axle for optimal weight distribution. A MaxxECU engine management system wired in with a custom loom gives the firing orders.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/15064525/ISB-Alec-Pender-Speedhunters-561-680x1020.jpg\" alt=\"ISB - Alec Pender - Speedhunters -56\" data-attachment-id=\"654019\" data-go-fullscreen=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/15064525/ISB-Alec-Pender-Speedhunters-561.jpg\" data-can-print=\"true\" data-attachment-url=\"https://www.speedhunters.com/2024/10/a-ferrari-v8-powered-celica/isb-alec-pender-speedhunters-56-2/\" data-src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/15064525/ISB-Alec-Pender-Speedhunters-561-1200x1800.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/15064700/ISB-Alec-Pender-Speedhunters-1351-680x1020.jpg\" alt=\"ISB - Alec Pender - Speedhunters -135\" data-attachment-id=\"654033\" data-go-fullscreen=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/15064700/ISB-Alec-Pender-Speedhunters-1351.jpg\" data-can-print=\"true\" data-attachment-url=\"https://www.speedhunters.com/2024/10/a-ferrari-v8-powered-celica/isb-alec-pender-speedhunters-135-2/\" data-src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/15064700/ISB-Alec-Pender-Speedhunters-1351-1200x1800.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/15064706/ISB-Alec-Pender-Speedhunters-1341-680x1020.jpg\" alt=\"ISB - Alec Pender - Speedhunters -134\" data-attachment-id=\"654034\" data-go-fullscreen=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/15064706/ISB-Alec-Pender-Speedhunters-1341.jpg\" data-can-print=\"true\" data-attachment-url=\"https://www.speedhunters.com/2024/10/a-ferrari-v8-powered-celica/isb-alec-pender-speedhunters-134-2/\" data-src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/15064706/ISB-Alec-Pender-Speedhunters-1341-1200x1800.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/15064654/ISB-Alec-Pender-Speedhunters-1361-680x453.jpg\" alt=\"ISB - Alec Pender - Speedhunters -136\" data-attachment-id=\"654032\" data-go-fullscreen=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/15064654/ISB-Alec-Pender-Speedhunters-1361.jpg\" data-can-print=\"true\" data-attachment-url=\"https://www.speedhunters.com/2024/10/a-ferrari-v8-powered-celica/isb-alec-pender-speedhunters-136-2/\" data-src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/15064654/ISB-Alec-Pender-Speedhunters-1361-1200x800.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/15064712/ISB-Alec-Pender-Speedhunters-1331-680x453.jpg\" alt=\"ISB - Alec Pender - Speedhunters -133\" data-attachment-id=\"654035\" data-go-fullscreen=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/15064712/ISB-Alec-Pender-Speedhunters-1331.jpg\" data-can-print=\"true\" data-attachment-url=\"https://www.speedhunters.com/2024/10/a-ferrari-v8-powered-celica/isb-alec-pender-speedhunters-133-2/\" data-src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/15064712/ISB-Alec-Pender-Speedhunters-1331-1200x800.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/15064718/ISB-Alec-Pender-Speedhunters-1321-680x453.jpg\" alt=\"ISB - Alec Pender - Speedhunters -132\" data-attachment-id=\"654036\" data-go-fullscreen=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/15064718/ISB-Alec-Pender-Speedhunters-1321.jpg\" data-can-print=\"true\" data-attachment-url=\"https://www.speedhunters.com/2024/10/a-ferrari-v8-powered-celica/isb-alec-pender-speedhunters-132-2/\" data-src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/15064718/ISB-Alec-Pender-Speedhunters-1321-1200x800.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/15064411/ISB-Alec-Pender-Speedhunters-53-680x453.jpg\" alt=\"ISB - Alec Pender - Speedhunters -53\" data-attachment-id=\"654018\" data-go-fullscreen=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/15064411/ISB-Alec-Pender-Speedhunters-53.jpg\" data-can-print=\"true\" data-attachment-url=\"https://www.speedhunters.com/2024/10/a-ferrari-v8-powered-celica/isb-alec-pender-speedhunters-53/\" data-src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/15064411/ISB-Alec-Pender-Speedhunters-53-1200x800.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/15064724/ISB-Alec-Pender-Speedhunters-1311-680x453.jpg\" alt=\"ISB - Alec Pender - Speedhunters -131\" data-attachment-id=\"654037\" data-go-fullscreen=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/15064724/ISB-Alec-Pender-Speedhunters-1311.jpg\" data-can-print=\"true\" data-attachment-url=\"https://www.speedhunters.com/2024/10/a-ferrari-v8-powered-celica/isb-alec-pender-speedhunters-131-2/\" data-src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/15064724/ISB-Alec-Pender-Speedhunters-1311-1200x800.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003eThe Celica rides on Italian-made 18-inch NTM wheels wrapped in Hankook full slicks. Behind the wheels, Ferrari 360 hubs hold Ferrari brakes, managed by a fully custom pedal box and brake biasing system.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/15064759/ISB-Alec-Pender-Speedhunters-2001-680x453.jpg\" alt=\"ISB - Alec Pender - Speedhunters -200\" data-attachment-id=\"654042\" data-go-fullscreen=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/15064759/ISB-Alec-Pender-Speedhunters-2001.jpg\" data-can-print=\"true\" data-attachment-url=\"https://www.speedhunters.com/2024/10/a-ferrari-v8-powered-celica/isb-alec-pender-speedhunters-200-2/\" data-src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/15064759/ISB-Alec-Pender-Speedhunters-2001-1200x800.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003eWith a full tank of fuel and Alessio on board, the Ferrari-powered Toyota weighs 1,100kg (2,425lb). That’s a good effort, considering all glass windows except for the polycarbonate windscreen have been retained.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/15064846/ISB-Alec-Pender-Speedhunters-2121-680x453.jpg\" alt=\"ISB - Alec Pender - Speedhunters -212\" data-attachment-id=\"654050\" data-go-fullscreen=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/15064846/ISB-Alec-Pender-Speedhunters-2121.jpg\" data-can-print=\"true\" data-attachment-url=\"https://www.speedhunters.com/2024/10/a-ferrari-v8-powered-celica/isb-alec-pender-speedhunters-212-2/\" data-src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/15064846/ISB-Alec-Pender-Speedhunters-2121-1200x800.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/15064815/ISB-Alec-Pender-Speedhunters-2031-680x1020.jpg\" alt=\"ISB - Alec Pender - Speedhunters -203\" data-attachment-id=\"654045\" data-go-fullscreen=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/15064815/ISB-Alec-Pender-Speedhunters-2031.jpg\" data-can-print=\"true\" data-attachment-url=\"https://www.speedhunters.com/2024/10/a-ferrari-v8-powered-celica/isb-alec-pender-speedhunters-203-2/\" data-src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/15064815/ISB-Alec-Pender-Speedhunters-2031-1200x1800.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/15064821/ISB-Alec-Pender-Speedhunters-2041-680x1020.jpg\" alt=\"ISB - Alec Pender - Speedhunters -204\" data-attachment-id=\"654046\" data-go-fullscreen=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/15064821/ISB-Alec-Pender-Speedhunters-2041.jpg\" data-can-print=\"true\" data-attachment-url=\"https://www.speedhunters.com/2024/10/a-ferrari-v8-powered-celica/isb-alec-pender-speedhunters-204-2/\" data-src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/15064821/ISB-Alec-Pender-Speedhunters-2041-1200x1800.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003cp\u003eAfter three thousand hours of relentless work, Alessio unveiled a tyre-melting, rear-engined, rear-wheel-drive Celica that’s about as far removed from the original example that ignited his interest in the model.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ciframe title=\"YouTube video player\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/mRBQ-8TzEW0?si=x7a1APxJRa_1EfDA\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"\u003e\u003c/iframe\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThis is not just another cross-manufacturer repower thrown together with whatever off-the-shelf parts. It’s an entirely new vehicle, with nearly every component reimagined. Alessio’s wild Celica is a testament to what can be achieved in a home garage, fueled by passion and a helping hand from family.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eAlec Pender\u003c/strong\u003e\u003cbr/\u003e\nInstagram: \u003ca href=\"https://www.instagram.com/noplansco/\" target=\"_blank\"\u003enoplansco\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\t\t\u003c/div\u003e\n\t\n\t\n\n\t\u003cdiv\u003e\n\t\t\u003cp\u003e\n\t\t\t\u003ch3\u003eOFFICIAL SPEEDHUNTERS SUPPLIERS\u003c/h3\u003e\n\t\t\u003c/p\u003e\n\t\t\n\t\u003c/div\u003e\n\n  \u003c/section\u003e\u003c/div\u003e",
